\f2\fs26 \cf0 # Customer Churn Prediction ML Pipeline\
\
End-to-end machine learning project predicting customer churn using XGBoost classification.\
\
## 
\f5 \uc0\u55357 \u56522 
\f2  Project Overview\
\
- **Objective:** Predict which customers are likely to churn\
- **Dataset:** [Telecom churn dataset] (~7,000 customers, 21 features)\
- **Best Model:** XGBoost Classifier\
